    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h2 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-IntegratedPrintingwithQZTray\">Integrated Printing with QZ Tray</h2><p>Integrated Printing in RepairQ uses an open-source software application called QZ to communicate directly with printers without involving browser print dialog. Listed below are the system requirements needed to run QZ. Please do not attempt to use this integration with devices that do not meet the minimum requirements. For an introduction to QZ printing along with additional resources and tutorials, <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229707/QZ+Integrated+Printing+-+Start+Here\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229707\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">start here</a>!</p><h3 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229707/QZ+Integrated+Printing+-+Start+Here\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229707\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Introduction to QZ Integrated Printing - Start Here!</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936949301/Integrated+Printing+Troubleshooting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936949301\" data-linked-resource-version=\"17\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Printing Troubleshooting</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933869057/Recommended+Hardware+Troubleshooting+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933869057\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Recommended Hardware Troubleshooting Resources</a> </p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936588827/Technical%20-%20124a6d.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-QZSystemRequirements\">QZ System Requirements</h2><p>Minimum requirements are pulled directly from QZ's support site: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://qz.io/wiki/faq#java-versions\" rel=\"nofollow\">QZ Wiki - FAQ</a>.</p><h2 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-JavaVersions\">Java Versions</h2><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"046fbb58-9495-475e-8f5c-e88b1597e604\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Product</strong></p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Minimum</strong> <strong>Version</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>QZ Tray 2.2</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>OpenJDK 11 (bundled)</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>QZ Tray 2.1</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Java 8 / OpenJDK 1.8*</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>QZ Tray 2.0</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Java 7 / OpenJDK 1.7*</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>QZ Tray 1.9</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Java 7 / OpenJDK 1.7</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>QZ Print 1.9</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Java 6 / OpenJDK 1.6</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Note: </strong>HTML printing in QZ Tray 2.x requires Java 8 + Java FX. Make sure you have the 64-bit version on Windows - <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://javadl.oracle.com/webapps/download/AutoDL?BundleId=218833_e9e7ea248e2c4826b92b3f075a80e441\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download Here</a>.</p><h2 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-OperatingSystems\">Operating Systems</h2><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"e4bfabe6-65fb-48ca-893d-e9a5357e199c\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Operating System</strong></p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Minimum Version</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Apple OS X</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>OS X 10.7 Lion or higher*</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Microsoft Windows</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Windows XP or higher*</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Linux</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Ubuntu 12.04 Precise or higher</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Note: </strong>QZ version 2.0 or higher requires 512MB of free memory (RAM) and recommends 6GB\u00a0or higher total system memory for raster graphics.</p><p>*Safari 5.1.7 is bundled with Lion but is not supported. An alternate browser is required.<br/>*Windows XP requires manual certificate installation. This will prompt when installing.</p><h2 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-WebBrowsers\">Web Browsers</h2><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"af270bb8-e571-4779-862d-6ff1cfd7eeac\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Web Browser</strong></p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Minimum Version</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Safari</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Safari 6.0.3 or higher</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Firefox</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Firefox 31 or higher*</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Chrome</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Chrome 31 or higher</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Internet Explorer</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>IE 10 or higher*</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Microsoft Edge</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>20.x or higher*</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><ul><li><p>Firefox requires a <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://qz.io/wiki/using-qz-tray#firefox-steps\" rel=\"nofollow\">browser restart for HTTPS</a>.</p></li><li><p>IE/Edge on domain networks requires external DNS access to locaalhost.qz.io due to a <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/qzind/qz-print/issues/39#issue-87042860\" rel=\"nofollow\">Local Intranet Limitation</a>.</p></li></ul><h2 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-RecommendedPrinterSettings\">Recommended Printer Settings</h2><p>When <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936457750\" rel=\"nofollow\">adding an integrated printer</a>, you\u2019ll add information regarding your paper settings. Below are printer settings that have worked for our users.</p><h3 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-StarReceiptPrinter\">Star Receipt Printer</h3><p><strong>Operating System</strong>: Windows 7 and 10</p><p><strong>Web Browser</strong>: Chrome</p><p><strong>Printer Type</strong>: Receipt\u00a0</p><p><strong>Printer Make/Model</strong>: Star TSP100</p><p><strong>Paper Width</strong>: 72</p><p><strong>Paper Height</strong>: 2000</p><p><strong>Printer DPI</strong>: 8\u00a0</p><p><strong>Unit of Measurement</strong>: millimeters</p><p /><p><strong>Operating System</strong>: Windows</p><p><strong>Web Browser</strong>: Chrome\u00a0</p><p><strong>Printer</strong> <strong>Type</strong>: Receipt\u00a0</p><p><strong>Printer Make/Model</strong>: Star TSP100 Cutter (TSP143)</p><p><strong>Paper Width</strong>: 72 (Actual paper width is 57mm)</p><p><strong>Paper Height</strong>: 200\u00a0</p><p><strong>Margin Top</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Right</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Bottom</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin</strong> <strong>Left</strong>: 20</p><p><strong>Unit of Measurement</strong>: millimeters</p><h3 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-EpsonReceiptPrinter\">Epson Receipt Printer</h3><p><strong>Operating System</strong>: Windows 11 and macOS Ventura 13.6.3</p><p><strong>Web Browser</strong>: Chrome</p><p><strong>Printer</strong> <strong>Type</strong>: Receipt\u00a0</p><p><strong>Printer Make/Model</strong>: Epson TM-T88V</p><p><strong>Paper Width</strong>: 72</p><p><strong>Margin Top</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Right</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Bottom</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin</strong> <strong>Left</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Unit of Measurement</strong>: millimeters</p><h3 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-BrotherLaserPrinter\">Brother Laser Printer</h3><p><strong>Operating System</strong>: Windows 7 and 10</p><p><strong>Web Browser</strong>: Chrome</p><p><strong>Printer Type</strong>: Desktop</p><p><strong>Printer Make/Model</strong>: Brother HL-L2305</p><p><strong>Paper Width</strong>: 8.5</p><p><strong>Paper Height</strong>: 11</p><p><strong>Actual Paper Size</strong>: 8.5 x 11 \u00a0</p><p><strong>Margin Top</strong>: 0\u00a0</p><p><strong>Margin Right</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Bottom</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Left</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Printer DPI</strong>: 600</p><p><strong>Unit of Measurement</strong>: inches</p><p><strong>Orientation</strong>: portrait</p><p><strong>Scale to Fit</strong>: yes</p><h3 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-BrotherLabelPrinter\">Brother Label Printer</h3><p><strong>Operating System</strong>: macOS 10.12.2</p><p><strong>Web Browser</strong>: Chrome</p><p><strong>Printer Type</strong>: Label</p><p><strong>Printer Make/Model</strong>: Brother QL-700</p><p><strong>Paper Width</strong>: 29</p><p><strong>Paper Height</strong>: 90</p><p><strong>Actual Paper Size</strong>: \u00a0 \u00a0</p><p><strong>Margin Top</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Right</strong>: 2</p><p><strong>Margin Bottom</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Left</strong>: 2</p><p><strong>Printer DPI</strong>: 12</p><p><strong>Unit of Measurement</strong>: millimeters</p><p><strong>Orientation</strong>: Portrait</p><p><strong>Scale to Fit</strong>: Yes</p><h3 id=\"QZPrintingSystemRequirementsandPrinterSettings-DymoLabelPrinter\">Dymo Label Printer</h3><p><strong>Operating System</strong>: macOS 10.12</p><p><strong>Web Browser</strong>: Chrome</p><p><strong>Printer Type</strong>: Label</p><p><strong>Printer Make/Model</strong>: Dymo 450 Turbo</p><p><strong>Paper Width</strong>: 2.31</p><p><strong>Paper Height</strong>: 4.00</p><p><strong>Actual Paper Size</strong><em>: </em>2.25 x 1.25 (Dymo 30334)</p><p><strong>Margin Top</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Right</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Bottom</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Left</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Printer DPI</strong>: 300</p><p><strong>Unit of Measurement</strong>: Inches</p><p><strong>Orientation</strong>: Portrait</p><p><strong>Scale</strong> <strong>to Fit</strong>: Yes</p><p /><p><strong>Operating System</strong>: Windows 10</p><p><strong>Web Browser</strong>: Chrome</p><p><strong>Printer Type</strong>: Label</p><p><strong>Printer Make/Model</strong>: Dymo LabelWriter 450/450Turbo\u00a0</p><p><strong>Paper</strong> <strong>Width</strong>: 2.4</p><p><strong>Paper Height</strong>: 3.00</p><p><strong>Actual Paper Size</strong>: 1 1/8 x 3 1/2 \u00a0(30252 labels)</p><p><strong>Margin Top</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Right</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Bottom</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Margin Left</strong>: 0</p><p><strong>Printer DPI</strong>: 300</p><p><strong>Unit of Measurement</strong>: inches</p><p><strong>Orientation</strong>: Reverse landscape</p><p><strong>Scale to Fit</strong>: no</p><p /><p><strong>Operating System: </strong>macOS 10.12</p><p><strong>Web Browser: </strong>Chrome</p><p><strong>Printer Type: </strong>Label</p><p><strong>Printer Make:\u00a0</strong>DYMO</p><p><strong>Printer Model: </strong>LabelWrite<strong>\u00a0</strong>450/450 Turbo</p><p><strong>Paper Width:\u00a0</strong>50.00</p><p><strong>Paper Height:\u00a0</strong>50.00</p><p><em><strong>Actual Paper Size:\u00a0</strong>DYMO 30336 (1&quot; x 2-1/8&quot;)</em></p><p><strong>Margin Top:\u00a0</strong>26.00</p><p><strong>Margin Right:\u00a0</strong>0.00</p><p><strong>Margin Bottom:\u00a0</strong>0.00</p><p><strong>Margin Left:\u00a0</strong>0.00</p><p><strong>Printer DPI:\u00a0</strong>12</p><p><strong>Unit of Measurement:\u00a0</strong>millimeters</p><p><strong>Orientation:\u00a0</strong>landscape</p><p><strong>Scale to Fit:\u00a0</strong>yes</p><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
